\begin_inset Formula $C\left(\left[0,\infty\right),\mathbb{R}\right)$
\end_inset

 equipped with the measures 
\begin_inset Formula $P^{x}$
\end_inset

 above
\begin_inset Foot
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Which as discussed are product measures on a function space.
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

